data.name: ResetError
data.value: Can't get current object as MoveNext hasn't been called after Reset.

data.name: InvalidOperationError
data.value: There is no current entry. Either BTree had been modified by Add, Remove or Clear methods or MoveFirst or Search methods haven't been executed to make a valid Current entry.

data.name: MemAllocError
data.value: Possible cause of exception is out of memory.

data.name: NoComparerError
data.value: No comparer object was assigned to this BTree instance and no default comparer is suited to the collectible items.

data.name: KeysAndValuesDifferInSizeError
data.value: Number of Keys are not the same as number of Values.

data.name: SlotLengthDeSerializeError
data.value: "SlotLength" DeSerialization error. Invalid SlotLength was detected.

data.name: CurrentSortOrderDeSerializeError
data.value: "CurrentSortOrder" DeSerialization error. Invalid Sort Order was detected.

data.name: ComparerDeSerializeError
data.value: "Comparer" DeSerialization error. Invalid Comparer object was detected.

data.name: StartIndexIsGreaterThanLength
data.value: StartIndex is equal to or greater than the length of the destination array.

data.name: BTreeHasMoreElems
data.value: Number of items in the btree has exceeded number of elements in destination array starting from StartIndex.
